frameDefinitions: The Sleeper stays in an altered state of consciousness with greatly reduced external awareness.
An Agent causes Air to move in a direction, usually specifying either in or out of the body.
This frame is  concerned with the percepts that vibrations which travel through the air or another medium produce in hearing organs.
A Competition comes to an end, with a Competitor tying, winning, or losing against an Opponent (or opponents) according to their Score.
An Excreter excretes Excreta. 'Principal Skinner burped on me.'
A Cognizer calls up an episodic memory of past Experience or an Impression of a Salient_entity formed  on the basis of past experience.
frameExamples: I awoke to the <t>clash</t> of a jackhammer on concrete.
Unbelievable--he <t>lost</t> the gold medal by just .02 points!
Kozmo could <t>remember</t> when his modem was the fastest he could buy.
listRoleDefinitions: The entity that is sleeping.
This role identifies the <fen>Time</fen> when the sleep occurs.
Where the event takes place.
The <fen>Agent</fen>'s breathing causes the motion of the <fen>Air</fen>.  <fen>Agent</fen> is generally the External Argument.
<fen>Air</fen> is the substance that the <fen>Agent</fen> causes to move.
The time at which breathing occurs.
This role identifies the <fen>Place</fen> where the breathing occurs.
An entity that is construed as a single point source emitting sound.

The location at which sound is produced. This role differs from Location_of_sound_source in that it does not highlight the sound's spreading from its source to the perceiver's location, which is usually indicated by the preposition 'from'.
The individual involved in the <fen>Competition</fen>.
The individual that the <fen>Competitor</fen> has been competing against.
The individuals who compete against each other.
The event in which the <fen>Competitors</fen> compete with each other.
The time at which the <fen>Competition</fen> takes place.
The location at which the <fen>Competition</fen> takes place.
The <fen>Excreta</fen> is the waste expelled by the body.
The <fen>Excreter</fen> is the agent who excretes the <fen>Excreta</fen>.
The <fen>Source</fen> is the starting point of the <fen>Excreta</fen>'s motion.
When the <fen>Excreter</fen> engages in excretion.
This role identifieis the <fen>Place</fen> where the excretion occurs.
A person who recalls memories of past experience or impressions.
A person or thing that the <fen>Cognizer</fen> remembers as being involved in some state or event or as having some property.
A past event or state that the <fen>Cognizer</fen> witnessed and is now recalling. The <fen>Experience</fen> may be a specific event or state or a vaguer period that is treated as a unit.

A property that the <fen>Cognizer</fen> attributes to the <fen>Salient_entity</fen> based on their past experience of the <fen>Salient_entity</fen> or a category to which the <fen>Salient_entity</fen> is assigned.
A property or role that a <fen>Salient_entity</fen> actually held and which frames the memories that the <fen>Cognizer</fen> has of the <fen>Salient_entity</fen>.
The time when the <fen>Cognizer</fen> remembers the experience.
listRoleExamples: All I know is that he was still breathing <fex>at 2AM</fex>.
Lee breathed with difficulty <fex>on the track</fex>.
He woke up because of the blare <fex>of a car horn</fex>.
There was a clatter of running feet <fex>in the street outside</fex>.
Dr. Nick vomited <fex>puke</fex> across the table.
I will truly miss Delmar and <fex>I</fex> will always remember when his eyes lit up everytime he got ice-cream.
today I saw a sister's exclassmate, and didn't recognise him, I remember <fex>him</fex> taller.
I can still remember <fex>saying the pledge every morning before class in elementary school</fex>, a rare occurrence among elementary school kids nowadays.
I remember Peter <fex>as immensely kind in those first three weeks before I was packed off to boarding school</fex>.
Atulprasad is principally remembered <fex>as a musician and composer</fex>.
